      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of character, but overall it looks great and runs like a dream. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is complemented by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically robust, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the paint shows minor road patina consistent with its age, the chassis remains stiff and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A true enthusiast's spec optimized for performance longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
