      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers the perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road-wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, the cabin is strictly smoke-free, and all dual-zone climate controls and infotainment features function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly thanks to a documented history of synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of premium all-season tires and a complete brake service. It is a reliable, turn-key vehicle that has been cared for with an eye for detail.",
